br />\n<br />\n我星期四去,人比較少<br />\n<br />\n一開波衝哈利(30min),行埋史路比,LUNCH再去蜘蛛俠(唔洗等)同飛天翼龍(等40min)<br />\n<br />\n如果你假期去就要買,check日本假期"},{"pid":"8af046eb92c5df146bcb349e43014981fad77186","tid":571354,"uid":48117,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T03:18:44.000Z","msg":"前年暑假去過<br />\n同樓主一樣感覺，人地日本做得咁好<br />\n香港啲樂園真係差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無買快證，一早排隊狗衝左哈利波特同過山車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住落勁大雨，啲本地友年證走曬，我近乎玩乜都唔洗排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後玩左三次哈利波特先捨得走<br />\n<br />\n利申：有迪士尼年證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03599b519309e02e9dcde17e7b1c90d42c3079b3","tid":571354,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"852ba15c440de97da5e8257458d555177485da43","tid":571354,"uid":101417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38ed70ff1997a952c83142545806fe2f0f896ce1","tid":571354,"uid":16270,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"532469819d19b8193c719f041d40741dc6c165ff","tid":571354,"uid":101417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T14:31:48.000Z","msg":"本身去過幾次，前幾日再去過，多左minions同哈利波特，原本無咩期望，但今次去完覺得真係感受到好好既樂園氣氛，兩個新主題整得好好，好多detail位，工作人員好投入，好多日本人都著晒兩個主題既服飾，雖然人太多無玩遊戲，但淨行淨睇感覺都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n反觀香港d所謂樂園，就算多唔多內地人都好，原本都係唔好玩，根本就無heart整，淨係歸咎唔夠大。<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 長期有年證"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T15:04:53.000Z","msg":"我同你講 香港人個園唔好玩 你一定有份"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T15:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T03:23:08.000Z","msg":"ON9到笑咗出嚟"},{"pid":"447659f513e5fd8bfd12a74e777a4a7bf0d7035a","tid":571354,"uid":675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T03:32:27.000Z","msg":"之前去個陣玩攤位贏左個公仔<br />\n跟住個日起碼有三個工作人員同我講話呢個公仔好得意喎 又讚我叻 又同我give me five<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係哈利波特個度買野比錢個陣又有工作人員聊我傾兩句<br />\n呢d互動唔會係香港見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw上次買左哈利波特個整理劵<br />\n編左係五六點入去 <br />\n但點解好似個個都入得 冇人check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我本身以為有人會check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}